title: Dak Prescott, CBA, Tom Brady, & free agency

description:
Colin discusses Dak Prescott getting the franchise tag, the new NFL CBA deal, the harsh reality for Tom Brady, and NFL free agency. Guests include Peter King, Joe Banner, Drew Bledsoe, and Jane Slater.
